title: 79: Bachelor in Paradise: The Finale
itunes:title: 79: Bachelor in Paradise: The Finale
description:
Time to say goodbye to 2019’s Bach nation run, Broads! But don’t worry - The Broads have a lot to say about it. They chat crying through all the Demi/Kristian scenes, thinking Clay and Nicole’s missing scene was our TV tripping (it wasn’t), JAYSHIA, Blake being a Veggie Tale castmate, the Van Life, our Kristina opinion, Dylan and Hannah becoming one entity, and much more! 
Be sure to continue tuning into our episodes! We promise we have some GOOD ones coming!
